{
  "texts": [
    "Computer vision is gaining popularity as a buzzword in the field of image processing.",
    "Human activity recognition (HAR), an established trend with numerous real-life applications including elderly care monitoring, rehabilitation activity tracking, posture correction analysis, and intrusion detection in security, is a prominent area of research in the field of computer vision (Singh and Vishwakarma 2019).",
    "Over the years, deep learning advances in computer vision have attracted the attention of many scholars in the field of human action recognition (Vishwakarma and Singh 2019; Singh and Vishwakarma 2021; Dhiman and Vishwakarma 2020).",
    "The convolutional neural network (CNN) is Xia Zhao and Limin Wang have contributed equally to this work.",
    "Extended author information available on the last page of the article used to construct the majority of computer vision algorithms."
  ]
}